[Shortcut](/wiki/Wikipedia:Shortcut "Wikipedia:Shortcut")* [WP:FA2016](https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Wikipedia:FA2016&redirect=no)

This page is the list of [featured articles](/wiki/Wikipedia:FA "Wikipedia:FA") that were promoted in 2016, listed by the month in which they were promoted. This list includes the date the article was featured on the main page (see [Wikipedia:Today's featured article](/wiki/Wikipedia:Today%27s_featured_article "Wikipedia:Today's featured article")) and the nominating user(s). Articles removed from featured status (see [Wikipedia:Former\_featured\_articles](/wiki/Wikipedia:Former_featured_articles "Wikipedia:Former featured articles")) are indicated in ~~strikethrough font~~. This page is used as input for [Wikipedia:List of Wikipedians by featured article nominations](/wiki/Wikipedia:List_of_Wikipedians_by_featured_article_nominations "Wikipedia:List of Wikipedians by featured article nominations").
